Starscream

Starscream patted Drillbit on the back.

"Alright. 3 votes for Phobia with 3 to go. The only way Phobia 
doesn't get it is if He, Dollen and Goldeneye vote for the same 
person. And if they do that were screwed. There would be no way to 
tie break. There would be on 5 votes, but not six. But one more vote 
for Phobia would ensure victory. Alright guys, what's your vote. You 
guys decided. I'm going to have a little rest. The pain's getting 
pretty heavy."

Starscream walked for a few metres saw a little pond through the 
bushes. He went to Octopus mode and went in. the water felt soothing. 
He was still within ear shot, so he could hear the last votes.
